A/IFRS17_P0550"><i>liability for incurred claims</i><ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0227"/></ph></xref>, comprising the fulfilment cash flows related to past service allocated to the group at that date, measured applying <xref id="IFRS17_X0180" base="F60991410" href="IFRS17_g33-35.dita#IFRS17_g33-35/IFRS17_g33-35_TI">paragraphs 33&#x2013;37</xref> and <xref id="IFRS17_X0181" base="F60991412" href="IFRS17_gB36-B119.dita#IFRS17_gB36-B119/IFRS17_gB36-B119_TI">B36&#x2013;B92</xref>.</p></li></ol></body></paragraph>